Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲妳還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.93,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，史派克，為我擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事別介意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是好好休息把感冒治好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.21,0:00:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.41,0:00:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳有沒有想要什麼?\N或是想吃什麼東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拿來給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃羅斯德的果實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅德斯的果實?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯德的果實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.66,0:00:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯德的果實就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在羅德斯春天才能採收的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種多汁爽口\N入口即化的水果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.79,0:01:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找到羅斯德的果實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.74,0:01:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳要乖乖的\N躺在床上休息，好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.81,0:01:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這非產季時\N為了他心愛的妮絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克找著羅斯德的果實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.55,0:01:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡、這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後他終於找到\N羅斯德之果所在的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯德的果實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯德的果實…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.94,0:01:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了!是羅斯德的果實!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!太好了妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，史派克真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪去拿羅斯德的果實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.85,0:01:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就告訴他\N那邊就有了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.99,0:01:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
